<!doctype html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">

    <title>Niels Gerritsen</title>

    <meta name="description" content="Hi, I develop for the web">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name='og:site_name' content='Niels Gerritsen'>
    <meta name='og:description' content='Hi, I develop for the web'>
    <meta name='og:image' content="images/screenshot.png">

    <link rel="icon" href="./images/favicon.png">

    <script src="js/bundle.js" async></script>

    <style>
    <%- fs.readFileSync(criticalCssPath) %>
    </style>

    <% var cssPaths = [
        'https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css',
        'https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:400,400italic,600'
    ] %>

    <% for (const path of cssPaths) { %>
        <link rel="preload" href="<%= path %>" as="style" onload="this.rel = 'stylesheet'">
    <% } %>

    <noscript>
    <% for (const path of cssPaths) { %>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= path %>">
    <% } %>
    </noscript>
</head>
<body>
    <!--[if lte IE 11]>
        <p class="browser-support-message">
            Sorry, but I do not support your browser.
            <a href="http://browsehappy.com/" target="_blank">Click here to upgrade your browser.</a>
        </p>
  <![endif]-->

    <nav class="top-bar">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="top-bar__content">
                <h1 class="top-bar__title">Niels Gerritsen</h1>
                <a
                    class="top-bar__link"
                    href="http://wecodetheweb.com"
                    target="_blank"
                    title="My webdevelopment blog"
                >
                    Blog
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="intro">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="intro__quote-circle">
                <p class="intro__quote">
                    Hi,<br>
                    <span class="intro__quote-big">I develop</span><br>
                    for the web<br>
                    ..
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <article class="padded-article">
                    <h3>Web development</h3>

                    <p>I develop for the web from front to back. My main expertise lies in front-end development. I'm a skilled HTML, CSS and Javascript developer. I am also capable of developing on the server side, using Node.js, PHP or C# ASP.NET. Last but not least I like to be involved in the design/UX process of a web application.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section section--code">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <article class="padded-article padded-article--odd">
                    <h3>Javascript</h3>

                    <p>I'm a Javascript enthusiast. It's the language that got me hooked on programming and is very important for the web. From designing a Javascript application architecture to implementing a new framework like React or Angular, I can do it. I'm a big advocate of <i>functional programming</i> practices in Javascript and in love with <i>ReactiveX</i>.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <article class="padded-article">
                    <h3>Learn</h3>

                    <p>I find constantly learning new things manditory for being a successful developer. If I need to learn some framework, language or method, I am eager and capable to learn it fast. This makes me flexible in finding new solutions.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>

        <section class="section section--dark">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <h2>Publications <small class="hidden visible-inline-from-lg">(hover for info)</small></h1>
                <ul class="publications">
                    <% for (const publication of [
                        {
                            title: 'De Sushimeisjes',
                            description: 'De Sushimeisjes (the Sushigirls) is a webshop based on Wordpress I developed. It features a clean, responsive design.',
                            url: 'https://www.desushimeisjes.nl',
                            thumbnail: 'desushimeisjes-thumb.jpg'
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'We code the web',
                            description: 'We code the web is a blog about front-end development, where I share my experiences and insights about web development.',
                            url: 'https://www.wecodetheweb.com',
                            thumbnail: 'wecodetheweb-thumb.jpg'
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'CareHR',
                            description: 'CareHR is a dutch company offering professional human resource advice in the health care sector. I made this clean and responsive informative website for CareHR.',
                            url: 'https://www.carehr.nl',
                            thumbnail: 'carehr-thumb.jpg'
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'Libsizes',
                            description: 'A web app with Node.js and React that calculates the sizes of Javascript libraries using Webpack. It runs on Heroku and is continuously deployed with Travis CI.',
                            url: 'https://libsizes.nielsgerritsen.com',
                            thumbnail: 'libsizes-thumb.jpg'
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'Timiks',
                            description: 'A Rubik\'s cube timer for speedsolvers, created using React, redux and styled-components. Optimized for adding to the homescreen of a phone as an app.',
                            url: 'https://timiks.com',
                            thumbnail: 'timiks-thumb.jpg'
                        },
                        {
                            title: 'NPM libraries',
                            description: 'I published some Javascript libraries on npm. Click the link to check them out.',
                            url: 'https://www.npmjs.com/~ngerritsen',
                            thumbnail: 'npm-thumb.jpg'
                        }
                    ]) { %>
                        <li class="publications__item">
                            <div
                                class="publication"
                                data-publication
                                data-publication-active-class="publication__meta--show"
                            >
                                <img src="images/<%- publication.thumbnail %>" alt="<%- publication.title %>" class="publication__image">
                                <div class="publication__meta" data-publication-meta>
                                    <h3 class="publication__title"><%- publication.title %></h3>
                                    <p class="publication__description">
                                        I published some Javascript libraries on npm. Click the link to check them out.
                                    </p>
                                    <a
                                        class="publication__link"
                                        href="<%- publication.url %>"
                                        target="_blank"
                                        title="<%- publication.title %>"
                                    >
                                        <%- publication.url.replace(/^https?:\/\//, ''); %>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="publication__toggle-wrapper hidden-from-lg">
                                    <button
                                      data-publication-toggle
                                      data-publication-toggle-active-content="<i class='button__icon fa fa-eye-slash'></i> Hide info"
                                      class="publication__toggle button button--primary button--small"
                                    >
                                        <i class="button__icon fa fa-eye"></i> Show info
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section section--grey">
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <article class="info">
                    <div class="info__portrait">
                        <img src="images/portrait.jpg" class="portrait-ball">
                    </div>

                    <div class="info__content">
                        <h2>Info</h2>

                        <p>My name is Niels Gerritsen, I am a <span data-age data-postfix=" year old "></span>software developer from The Netherlands. I specialize in front-end development, using modern frameworks and tooling like React, Angular, RxJS, Webpack and SASS.</p>

                        <p>I graduated with Industrial Product Design at The Hague University, but during my study I already I did a lot of web development in my spare time. After my graduation I started working as a software developer gaining a lot of experience in front- and back-end development.</p>

                        <p>
                            <a
                                href="https://twitter.com/NielsG89"
                                class="button button--primary button--list-item"
                                target="_blank"
                                title="Follow @NielsG89 on Twitter"
                            >
                                <i class="button__icon fa fa-twitter"></i> Follow
                            </a>
                            <a
                                href="https://www.linkedin.com/pub/niels-gerritsen/26/955/10b"
                                class="button button--primary button--list-item"
                                target="_blank"
                                title="Connect to Niels Gerritsen on LinkedIn"
                            >
                                <i class="button__icon fa fa-linkedin-square"></i> Connect
                            </a>
                            <a
                                href="https://github.com/ngerritsen"
                                class="button button--primary button--list-item"
                                target="_blank"
                                title="Check me out on GitHub"
                            >
                                <i class="button__icon fa fa-github"></i> Collab
                            </a>
                            <a  href="/files/cv-niels-gerritsen.pdf"
                                class="button button--success button--list-item"
                                download
                                title="Download my CV"
                            >
                                <i class="button__icon fa fa-file-text"></i>Curriculum Vitae
                            </a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

